220
00:22:58,079 --> 00:23:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ja njih pitan, momci, znate li vi što je to 6x7?

221
00:23:01,759 --> 00:23:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nemamo pojma.

222
00:23:02,799 --> 00:23:04,299
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zašto da to radite?

223
00:23:04,299 --> 00:23:07,259
[SPEAKER_00] Pa eto, to je onako foratata.

224
00:23:07,460 --> 00:23:14,220
