[SPEAKER_00] nije tata samo moj,

627
00:46:04,699 --> 00:46:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] nego tata je i od Ilije,

628
00:46:07,099 --> 00:46:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] i Filipa, i Daniela, i od Ive,

629
00:46:08,380 --> 00:46:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] i to je normalno,

630
00:46:10,980 --> 00:46:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] ona sad ulazi u taj dječaj egoizam,

631
00:46:12,599 --> 00:46:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] i sad je jako bitna stvar,

632
00:46:14,099 --> 00:46:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] da mi ne padnemo u tu zamku,

633
00:46:15,860 --> 00:46:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] dječajeg egoizma,

634
00:46:17,039 --> 00:46:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji je prirodan,

635
00:46:18,039 --> 00:46:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji je normalan,

636
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] nego da mi tu

637
00:46:20,420 --> 00:46:22,599
