638
00:46:22,699 --> 00:46:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] u isto vrijeme postavimo granicu,

639
00:46:24,159 --> 00:46:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] tako da postavljanje granica,

640
00:46:26,420 --> 00:46:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] je jedna od najbitnijih stvari,

641
00:46:28,119 --> 00:46:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi u životu trebamo jedni prema drugima imati,

642
00:46:32,039 --> 00:46:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

643
00:46:33,619 --> 00:46:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] ljubite jedne druge,

644
00:46:34,559 --> 00:46:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] ko što sami sebe ljubite,

645
00:46:36,019 --> 00:46:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] to znači postaviti granicu prema drugima,

646
00:46:38,599 --> 00:46:39,800
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

647
00:46:39,800 --> 00:46:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja trebam sebe znati ljubiti,

648
00:46:41,539 --> 00:46:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] imati svoje samopouzdanje,

649
00:46:43,440 --> 00:46:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] samopoštovanje,

650
00:46:44,400 --> 00:46:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ja onda mogao drugu osobu ljubiti,

651
00:46:47,079 --> 00:46:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] kako će jedna majka ili jedan otac ljubiti svoje djete,

652
00:46:49,960 --> 00:46:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] ako od sebe ne ljubi,

653
00:46:51,880 --> 00:46:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] ne na onaj egoističan način,

654
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] ne na sebičan način,

655
00:46:55,139 --> 00:46:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego rečimo osoba je podređena drugome,

656
00:46:57,780 --> 00:47:00,139
[SPEAKER_00] i sve što drugi pomisli ta osoba radi,

657
00:47:00,139 --> 00:47:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] znači da zaboravljaš sebe,

658
00:47:02,280 --> 00:47:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] i zato je jako bitna stvar postavljati granice,

659
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] ima predivna knjiga,

660
00:47:06,380 --> 00:47:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] granice se zove knjiga,

661
00:47:07,579 --> 00:47:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] preporučio bih svakome da pročita,

662
00:47:09,480 --> 00:47:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] jako bitna stvar,

663
00:47:11,019 --> 00:47:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] u životu znat postaviti granice,

664
00:47:12,820 --> 00:47:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] i u partnerskim odnosima,

665
00:47:15,219 --> 00:47:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] u poslovnim odnosima,

666
00:47:16,460 --> 00:47:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] u prijateljskim odnosima,

667
00:47:17,699 --> 00:47:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] u braku,

668
00:47:18,420 --> 00:47:19,239
[SPEAKER_00] sa djecom,

669
00:47:19,239 --> 00:47:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] bilo, bilo gdje,

670
00:47:20,860 --> 00:47:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] prema roditeljima,

671
00:47:21,980 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] ništa to nije negativno,

672
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] ništa to nije loše,

673
00:47:24,800 --> 00:47:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] nije to nepoštivanje,

674
00:47:26,059 --> 00:47:27,760
[SPEAKER_00] to je baš istinsko poštivanje,

675
00:47:27,760 --> 00:47:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] jer, Marko,

676
00:47:29,320 --> 00:47:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja prelazim svaku tvoju granicu,

677
00:47:31,599 --> 00:47:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] i ti sve to prihvaćaš,

678
00:47:33,059 --> 00:47:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] zato što ja sam kao neki autoritet,

679
00:47:34,699 --> 00:47:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam stari od tebe,

680
00:47:35,719 --> 00:47:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje,

681
00:47:36,300 --> 00:47:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] ti ćeš za malo vremena postati nesiguran,

682
00:47:38,960 --> 00:47:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš baš biti sretan,

683
00:47:40,940 --> 00:47:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] počeš sebe mrzit,

684
00:47:43,079 --> 00:47:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] sebe ćeš početi preispetivati,

685
00:47:44,579 --> 00:47:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] i to rade manipulatori,

686
00:47:46,599 --> 00:47:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] narcisoidne osobe,

687
00:47:48,480 --> 00:47:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju potrebu,

688
00:47:49,300 --> 00:47:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] da neko oko njih skače,

689
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] misli o njima,

690
00:47:52,679 --> 00:47:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] i da su oni u centru pozornosti,

691
00:47:54,900 --> 00:47:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] pa imaju milion nekih pravila,

692
00:47:56,380 --> 00:47:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] i svega i svačega,

693
00:47:57,800 --> 00:47:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] zato treba tu biti jako prezvan,

694
00:47:59,559 --> 00:48:01,639
[SPEAKER_00] i treba znat postati granicu,

695
00:48:01,639 --> 00:48:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] i to je skroz ok imat granice.

696
00:48:03,400 --> 00:48:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] A kako ste vi sa svojim te mobiteli rješili,

697
00:48:05,579 --> 00:48:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] da već ste nešto spomenuli?

698
00:48:06,880 --> 00:48:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa jednostavno,

699
00:48:08,500 --> 00:48:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] smo mi to rješili,

700
00:48:09,199 --> 00:48:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] ja i žena smo razgovarali,

701
00:48:10,300 --> 00:48:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] bili, donijeli smo zajednu odluku,

702
00:48:12,000 --> 00:48:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] ako se završe sve zadaće,

703
00:48:13,820 --> 00:48:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] svi zadaci,

704
00:48:14,619 --> 00:48:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] vezan za školu i slično,

705
00:48:15,840 --> 00:48:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] imaju mogućnost,

706
00:48:17,159 --> 00:48:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] po pola sata Ilija,

707
00:48:18,300 --> 00:48:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] pola sata Filip,

708
00:48:19,219 --> 00:48:21,019
[SPEAKER_00] pet kuni subotom biti na mobitelu,

709
00:48:21,019 --> 00:48:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] nekad se to malo produži,

710
00:48:22,800 --> 00:48:25,300
[SPEAKER_00] ako su ekstra neke stvari dobro uradili,

711
00:48:25,300 --> 00:48:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] slično,

712
00:48:25,739 --> 00:48:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] i to je to.

713
00:48:27,639 --> 00:48:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se drže toga pravila,

714
00:48:29,420 --> 00:48:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo isto tu jako,

715
00:48:30,639 --> 00:48:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi reka, rigorozni,

716
00:48:32,340 --> 00:48:33,679
