[SPEAKER_00] pa nekad mogu i nedljom,

720
00:48:38,440 --> 00:48:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] ovako kad su ovi slobodni dan,

721
00:48:41,699 --> 00:48:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu bojišnjih praznika,

722
00:48:42,880 --> 00:48:43,340
