723
00:48:43,340 --> 00:48:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] onda je češće,

724
00:48:44,360 --> 00:48:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] ne previše često,

725
00:48:45,639 --> 00:48:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] nekad i,

726
00:48:46,179 --> 00:48:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

727
00:48:46,900 --> 00:48:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] nekad se zareda,

728
00:48:47,679 --> 00:48:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] deset dana zareda,

729
00:48:48,679 --> 00:48:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] nima je to ta danija.

730
00:48:51,860 --> 00:48:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi rekao,

731
00:48:52,940 --> 00:48:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji dalji u životu,

732
00:48:55,260 --> 00:48:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali vidimo posljedice,

733
00:48:56,860 --> 00:48:57,760
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo posljedice,

734
00:48:57,760 --> 00:48:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo da,

735
00:48:58,239 --> 00:48:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] nakon toga,

736
00:48:59,159 --> 00:49:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] oni su više razdražljivi,

737
00:49:00,480 --> 00:49:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] ljute za neke gluposti,

738
00:49:01,820 --> 00:49:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] teže se odvajaju mobitela,

739
00:49:03,380 --> 00:49:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje,

740
00:49:03,920 --> 00:49:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] što je skroz normalno,

741
00:49:05,159 --> 00:49:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] skroz normalno.

742
00:49:06,039 --> 00:49:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da mislim da tu,

743
