[SPEAKER_00] mame i tate moraju imati zajednički stav.

744
00:49:10,239 --> 00:49:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna je mama me nedavno rekla,

745
00:49:12,239 --> 00:49:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] taj je problem,

746
00:49:12,840 --> 00:49:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] kažu da,

747
00:49:13,500 --> 00:49:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja se toga držim,

748
00:49:14,780 --> 00:49:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali se ne držaju moji svekar i svekrva,

749
00:49:16,380 --> 00:49:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] moji mater i čača,

750
00:49:17,480 --> 00:49:18,820
[SPEAKER_00] sen toga ne držaju.

751
00:49:18,820 --> 00:49:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja govorim,

752
00:49:19,679 --> 00:49:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] pa to su tvoje djeca.

753
00:49:20,840 --> 00:49:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] I ako trebaš biti,

754
00:49:22,800 --> 00:49:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] to je ako ti i muž,

755
00:49:24,440 --> 00:49:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] trebate biti ti zliji,

756
00:49:26,260 --> 00:49:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] pogani ovakvi i onakvi,

757
00:49:28,239 --> 00:49:30,280
[SPEAKER_00] sin i čer,

758
00:49:30,280 --> 00:49:31,099
