761
00:49:33,699 --> 00:49:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ali postajte jasnu granicu.

762
00:49:35,880 --> 00:49:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možete davati mojoj djeci,

763
00:49:37,980 --> 00:49:40,579
